Package: BPpack
Title: Estimation of the prevalence of hypertention form blood pressure data allowing correction for within-person variability
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Edouard",
           family = "Chatignoux",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "edouard.chatignoux@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-9988-1108"))
Description: This package uses correction factor by age and sex estimated from NHANES III data to correct blood pressure measurments for visit to visit and within vist measurment error.  This correction alleviates bias in the estimation of the prevalence of hypertention in epidemiological studies.
